OL,3,CFour years after ITV News exposed:
OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FA council that left families in
OL,7,Fdangerous, uninhabitable homes has
OL,8,Fbeen taken out of special measures,
OL,9,Ffour years after ITV News exposed
OL,10,Fwidespread failings.
OL,12,FOur report inside a tower block on
OL,13,FRegina Road in South London in March
OL,14,F2021 led to national outrage, with the
OL,15,FPrime Minister condemning the
OL,16,Funinhabitable, unsafe conditions of
OL,17,Fhomes managed by Croydon Council and
OL,18,Fthe announcement of two independent
OL,19,Finvestigations.
