OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAn independent inquiry later concluded
OL,12,Fthe health of tenants was put at risk
OL,13,Fand that the council failed to keep
OL,14,Fthem safe.
OL,16,FThe Regulator for Social Housing
OL,17,Fconcluded the council had breached the
OL,18,Fsafety standards and placed into
OL,19,Fspecial measures.
