OL,3,CFour years after ITV News exposed:
OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,F"Taking into account the seriousness
OL,7,Fof the issues, the durations for which
OL,8,Ftenants were potentially exposed to
OL,9,Frisk, and the number of tenants
OL,10,Fpotentially affected, the regulator
OL,11,Fhas concluded that it is proportionate
OL,12,Fto find that LB Croydon has breached
OL,13,Fthe Home Standard and the Tenant
OL,14,FInvolvement and Empowerment Standard
OL,15,Fand that there was a risk of serious
OL,16,Fdetriment to tenants during this
OL,17,Fperiod", said the Regulator in May
OL,18,F2021.
