OL,4,CCroydon Council out of special measures
OL,6,FThe regeneration will deliver at least
OL,7,F225 new council homes, green spaces, a
OL,8,Fpreschool, and community facilities,
OL,9,Fsay the Council.
OL,11,FThe demolition of the first tower
OL,12,Fblock, 1-87 Regina Road, is underway
OL,13,Fand is expected to be completed by the
OL,14,Fautumn.
